[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    120[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mThe problem:[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;192;197;206m The code hardcodes [38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;163;190;140mmodel_id = "anthropic.claude-3-haiku"[38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;192;197;206m. If Haiku is unavailable (regional outage, quota exhausted, model deprecated), the entire pipeline stops. For a system processing patient messages with response time expectations, a fallback model strategy is worth mentioning.[K
